The exotic  Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel with 396 rooms. We are looking for a  Finance Coordinator to join the team.
The Finance Coordinator will assist in managing the administrative needs of the Finance Department and will liaise all the necessary documentation regarding the operations.
The ideal candidate must have the related background required for the position with at least 1-2 years work experience in the Hotel industry.
